  2→ * Milestone 3: Full Learning Lifecycle
  3→ *
  4→ * Traces: US-LL-03 (edit/deactivate), US-LL-04 (create with targeting)
  5→ *
  6→ * End-to-end lifecycle tests that combine creation with agent targeting,
